---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Dental Restoration" 
  category="Restorative Dentistry"
  description="Repair damaged teeth and restore comfortable eating with our comprehensive dental restoration services including fillings and more."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606811841689-23dfddce3e95?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Restore Your Comfort</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        When something doesn't feel right in your mouth, your daily eating routine can become uncomfortable. 
        We offer dental fillings for minimal tooth fractures, tooth decay and damaged surfaces of teeth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Common Restoration Needs
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Tooth Decay -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Tooth Decay</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Cavities caused by bacteria that weaken and create holes in tooth enamel
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tooth Fractures -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Tooth Fractures</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Chips, cracks, or breaks from trauma, grinding, or biting hard objects
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Surface Damage -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Surface Damage</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Worn surfaces from grinding, acid erosion, or normal wear over time
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Restoration Options
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Composite Fillings -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Tooth-Colored Fillings</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Composite resin fillings are made from a mixture of plastic and fine glass particles 
              that can be precisely matched to your tooth color.
            </p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advantages:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Natural appearance blends seamlessly</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Bonds directly to tooth structure</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Preserves more natural tooth structure</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Mercury-free and biocompatible</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-64 h-48 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Porcelain Inlays/Onlays -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="w-64 h-48 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">Porcelain Inlays & Onlays</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              For larger cavities or damaged areas, porcelain inlays and onlays provide superior 
              strength and aesthetics. They're custom-made in our lab for precision fit.
            </p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">When We Recommend:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Large cavities that are too big for fillings</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Cracked or fractured teeth needing reinforcement</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Replacing old, failing silver fillings</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span>Maximum strength and longevity needed</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibent text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Restoration Process
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">1</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Examination</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            We assess the damage and determine the best restoration approach
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">2</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Preparation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Local anesthetic and removal of decay or damaged tooth structure
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">3</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Restoration</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Precise placement of filling material or custom restoration
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">4</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Finishing</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Shaping, polishing, and bite adjustment for comfort
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Preventing Future Damage
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Daily Prevention</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Brush twice daily with fluoride toothpaste</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Floss daily to remove plaque between teeth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Use an antimicrobial mouthwash</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Limit sugary and acidic foods and drinks</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Professional Care</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Regular dental cleanings every 6 months</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Comprehensive exams for early detection</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Protective sealants for cavity-prone teeth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
            </div>
            <span>Custom night guards if you grind your teeth</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Don't Let Dental Problems Get Worse
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Early treatment of dental problems saves you time, money, and discomfort. 
        If you're experiencing tooth sensitivity or discomfort, don't wait to seek treatment.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Restoration Appointment
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/fillings" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Fillings</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cavity treatment and repair</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/crowns-bridges" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Crowns & Bridges</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Extensive restoration solutions</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/general-dentistry" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">General Dentistry</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Comprehensive dental care</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How do I know if I need a dental restoration?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Common signs include tooth sensitivity, pain when chewing, visible holes or dark spots in teeth, 
        rough or sharp edges, or food getting stuck in the same place repeatedly. A dental exam can 
        definitively determine if restoration is needed.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Are white fillings as strong as silver ones?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Modern composite (white) fillings are very durable and suitable for most cavities. While silver 
        amalgam may be slightly stronger for very large fillings, composite fillings offer superior 
        aesthetics and bond directly to teeth, often requiring less tooth removal.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will the restoration procedure hurt?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        We use local anesthetic to ensure you're comfortable during the procedure. Most patients 
        experience no pain during treatment. Some sensitivity is normal for a few days after, 
        but this usually resolves quickly.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long do dental restorations last?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Composite fillings typically last 5-7 years, while porcelain inlays/onlays can last 10-15 years 
        or more. Longevity depends on the size and location of the restoration, your oral hygiene, 
        and eating habits.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>